Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 奥兹马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都中弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这点擦伤
